FIG. 2 is a plan view of the valve of FIG. 1;


FIG. 3 is an elevation view of the aforesaid valve of FIG. 1;


FIG. 4 is an enlarged view of the valve of FIG. 1, shown in closed position;


and FIG. 5 is a view similar to that of FIG. 4, but with the valve shown in opening position.
